---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — NexPawn"
  description="Learn how NexPawn collects, uses and protects your personal information."
  lang="en"
  canonical="https://nexpawn.com/en/privacy-policy"
>
  <Navbar lang="en" />
  <main class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="last-updated">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <p>At NexPawn we value and respect the privacy of our users. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use and protect information when you use our platform.</p>

      <h2>1. Information we collect</h2>
      <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>

      <h3>a. User information:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Name</li>
        <li>Email address</li>
        <li>Login credentials</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>b. Information generated within the system:</h3>
      <ul>
        <li>Customer data entered by the user (names, ID, contact details)</li>
        <li>Pawn, transaction and operation records</li>
        <li>Cash register, purchase and sales records</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. Use of information</h2>
      <p>Collected information is used to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Provide and maintain NexPawn's operation</li>
        <li>Enable pawn shop management within the platform</li>
        <li>Improve user experience</li>
        <li>Provide technical support</li>
        <li>Send service-related communications</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Data responsibility</h2>
      <p>NexPawn acts as a software provider.</p>
      <p>The user is responsible for the data entered into the platform, including information about their own customers, and declares having the necessary authorization for its processing.</p>

      <h2>4. Storage and security</h2>
      <p>Information is stored on secure servers and reasonable measures are applied to protect data against unauthorized access, loss or alteration.</p>
      <p>However, no system is completely secure, so absolute security cannot be guaranteed.</p>

      <h2>5. User rights</h2>
      <p>The user may:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access their information</li>
        <li>Request correction or update</li>
        <li>Request deletion of their data</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise these rights, you may contact us via the email address indicated below.</p>

      <h2>6. Use of cookies</h2>
      <p>NexPawn may use cookies or similar technologies to improve user experience and analyze site usage.</p>

      <h2>7. Changes to this policy</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Changes will be published on this same page.</p>

      <h2>8. Contact</h2>
      <p>For questions related to this policy, you may write to:</p>
      <p><a href="mailto:contact@nexpawn.com">contact@nexpawn.com</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer lang="en" />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: 6rem 1.5rem 4rem;
    min-height: 60vh;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-blue-600, #1b63ff);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .last-updated {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted, #6b7280);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text, #111827);
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text, #111827);
    margin-top: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted, #374151);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  ul li {
    color: var(--color-text-muted, #374151);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--color-blue-600, #1b63ff);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
</style>
